Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.77,0:00:05.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:13.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.69,0:00:33.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.44,0:00:36.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The sound resonates\NInto my heart, so hard and deep
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:40.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A field of stars spans endlessly\NAnd through it I carve a passageway
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.35,0:00:42.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In step with time as generations change
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.39,0:00:44.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Close your eyes and listen closely
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.39,0:00:47.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shooting stars stream on silently…\Nuntil the goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.39,0:00:50.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep the light inside of you,\Nnever give up don't ever lose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.39,0:00:52.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Transcend time and you will prove,\Nthere is a special place for you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.27,0:00:54.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A blaze of glory is there,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.06,0:00:55.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's all a part of our estate;\Nlife is our story to create
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.85,0:01:01.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.77,0:01:05.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes speak from ages old by voice of light\NThroughout the age, never fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.69,0:01:09.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A secret fire, a scream of light,\Nvoices calling through twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.40,0:01:11.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cast your thoughts to the wind,\Nhang your wishes on the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.52,0:01:13.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Live your life with all your strength\Nfor dreams will reach you very soon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.48,0:01:16.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.06,0:01:19.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes speak from ages old\Nby voice of light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.27,0:01:21.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Throughout the age,\Nnever fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.39,0:01:24.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Someday your dream will find\Nits place somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.81,0:01:28.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep shining like a star
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.65,0:01:38.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?! Hey Ganju!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.07,0:01:41.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry, Sis…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.00,0:01:47.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I just showed him once.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.95,0:01:50.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined it would turn\Nout like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.75,0:01:51.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.95,0:02:08.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.33,0:02:11.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You did it, Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.50,0:02:12.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.66,0:02:17.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! Don't lose concentration!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.33,0:02:18.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.21,0:02:29.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you listening to me, idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.54,0:02:32.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you lose concentration,\Nyou’ll blow up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.56,0:02:33.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Didn’t I tell you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:35.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.62,0:02:37.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right!\NI tell you, you’re--!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.13,0:02:40.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’re just as guilty, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.84,0:02:43.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you, no food tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.24,0:02:46.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why put me together with him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.20,0:02:47.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Got any complaints?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.37,0:02:50.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yoruichi…?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.26,0:02:55.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So, Ichigo has finally completed\Na Cannonball?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.33,0:03:02.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh…? What’s wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.14,0:03:06.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing to worry about.\NHe’s only sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:08.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I want you all to sit over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:15.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo is asleep,\Nbut we haven’t got much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.16,0:03:17.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want to talk to you about\Nwhat you can expect
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.39,0:03:19.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,after we invade the Seireitei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:20.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You must--!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.91,0:03:24.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Practice hall
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.88,0:03:28.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fate of three sparrows,\Nfate of four dragons…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.42,0:03:32.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Blocked in from five directions,\Nunable to return six miles,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.02,0:03:33.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wind of the Heavens,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.82,0:03:35.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Orangutan, Spoons,\NCane of elm…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.65,0:03:41.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A thousand sprinkles of ash,\Na thousand bits…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.75,0:03:46.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,of wisdom…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:48.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,S-Silvervine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.82,0:03:54.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What… What the heck was\NI dreaming about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.35,0:03:55.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:04:02.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I sure slept well…or, did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.40,0:04:04.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing sleeping here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.29,0:04:06.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,“How should I know?” I said. Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.91,0:04:09.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are you doing, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.15,0:04:13.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s none of your business!\NGet lost, will you, dandelion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.87,0:04:14.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.88,0:04:20.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So, you’re finally up.\NIt’s time for us to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:22.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Leave…?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.79,0:04:28.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, so you’re all here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.18,0:04:29.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:31.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.89,0:04:35.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yoruichi, your tail looks like one\Nof those flexible toothbrushes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.39,0:04:37.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.39,0:04:37.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.62,0:04:39.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.32,0:04:43.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have\Na problem with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.92,0:04:48.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,N-No. It’s a beautiful tail, as always…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.95,0:04:51.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t you remember?!\NYou’re responsible for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:53.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:54.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.99,0:04:57.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It took the three of us…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.22,0:04:58.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,to finally get you to let go, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.81,0:05:03.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.85,0:05:07.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My tail…the tail I was so proud of…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.19,0:05:11.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’d be smart to stay away\Nfrom that subject!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.50,0:05:13.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,G-Got it…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.24,0:05:17.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What happened to Ganju?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.28,0:05:19.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I dunno…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.29,0:05:22.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He was muttering about\Nsomething downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.13,0:05:23.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:31.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The hero always arrives last.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.61,0:05:34.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What’s with that getup?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.37,0:05:39.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s my very own battle costume.\NDon’t I look cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:41.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cry and beg all you want,\Nbut I won’t lend it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:42.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How do you like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.33,0:05:44.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Battle costume?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.92,0:05:46.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What’s it for,\Nif you’re just seeing us off?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:05:59.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A Soul Reaper killed my big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.33,0:06:02.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ganju! Why you…!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.04,0:06:05.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just shut up and listen, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.33,0:06:11.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My brother…was a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:16.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He managed to pass the Soul Reaper\N Academy entrance exam in one try.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.19,0:06:19.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At that time, his spiritual power\Nwas at Level 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.17,0:06:23.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s the same level as a lieutenant\Nof the 13 Court Guarding Squads.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.00,0:06:28.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then, he finished\Nsix years’ curriculum in one,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:29.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and he became a member\Nof a Squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:32.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In just five years,\Nhe became a lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.29,0:06:35.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But my brother was killed…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.27,0:06:39.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,betrayed by his Soul Reaper comrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.31,0:06:44.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was still a kid back then,\Nso I don’t remember the details,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.14,0:06:48.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but there are two things\NI’ll never forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.99,0:06:51.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Their faces…! Two faces!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.45,0:06:56.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The ogre-like face of that Soul Reaper
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:06:58.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,who dragged my badly injured\Nand dying brother home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.12,0:07:03.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And the face of my brother as he\Nhappily gave thanks to that Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.95,0:07:08.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why did my brother do that?\NWhy did he seem so happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.02,0:07:10.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To this day, I don’t know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.56,0:07:13.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But there’s one thing I can say…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.14,0:07:19.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My brother didn’t blame Soul Reapers.\NHe didn’t hate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.91,0:07:22.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew he had such\Na painful experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.24,0:07:24.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.70,0:07:27.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn’t my brother\Ndespise Soul Reapers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.53,0:07:30.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why did he continue to trust\Nin the Soul Reapers?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.63,0:07:35.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’re not like the other Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.53,0:07:38.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I owe her…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:44.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She saved my life.\NAnd I haven’t repaid her yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.09,0:07:53.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to turn into a pitiful guy\Nwho'd turn his back on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.96,0:07:56.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.67,0:08:00.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I go with you,\NI might discover something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:02.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.59,0:08:06.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why I’m gonna help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.93,0:08:13.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll go as far as I can, to see what\Na Soul Reaper is really like!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.59,0:08:15.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ganju…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.76,0:08:19.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You’re really something, Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:21.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ganju…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.42,0:08:23.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’ve grown up fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.28,0:08:27.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Humph! Looks like you’ve\Nmade up your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.24,0:08:33.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I work with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:35.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.24,0:08:40.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone…\Nare you ready for the Cannonball?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:41.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:44.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? By the way…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.20,0:08:44.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.06,0:08:46.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yoruichi, can you make\Nthe Cannonball?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.97,0:08:51.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I wonder…\NLet me try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:55.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t tell me…\Nthis is your first try?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:08:58.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, put that down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:10.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Humph!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.03,0:09:14.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Something like this is\Nas simple as breathing in and out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:20.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! It took us so long\Nto learn to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.86,0:09:22.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you resent it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:24.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you resent that I could\Neasily do something
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.55,0:09:28.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that gave you so much trouble\Nto accomplish? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.37,0:09:31.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ganju.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:35.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Were you able to master it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.92,0:09:36.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I guess…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.25,0:09:40.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then we’ll go with Flower-Crane\NCannon Launch Method Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.06,0:09:40.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Can you handle it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.92,0:09:41.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.09,0:09:48.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t you chicken out and run off\Nin the middle of it now, damn brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.20,0:09:49.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sis…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.58,0:09:52.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you’re gonna go,\Nyou’ve got to put your life on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.62,0:09:53.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.29,0:09:57.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.07,0:10:00.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There’ll be no more delays,\Nyou brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.86,0:10:05.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now, get in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.73,0:10:12.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The sun will be rising soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.70,0:10:15.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That will be the signal to begin\Nthe launching ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.45,0:10:28.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Listen… Once we’re in the Seireitei,\Nwe have to stick together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.92,0:10:31.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you encounter any Captains,\Ndon’t think, just run.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.05,0:10:35.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Our goal is to save Rukia,\Nand nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.86,0:10:39.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t, by any means,\Ntake any useless risks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.62,0:11:01.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In the distance!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.90,0:11:06.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Copper-hued greed desires\N36 degrees of dominance!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.45,0:11:09.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It has begun!\NPour in your spiritual energies!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:17.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,72 pairs of illusions,\N13 pairs of horns,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.99,0:11:22.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The monkey’s right paw\Ncaptures a star!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:40.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Held in the embrace of 25 suns,\Nthe cradle of sand will flow with blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.80,0:11:46.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Flower-Crane Cannon Launch\NMethod Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.83,0:11:47.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kagizaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.45,0:11:57.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You have done it, Lady Kukaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.76,0:11:59.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.87,0:12:09.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Go with care…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:11.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ganju.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.40,0:12:32.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ohh…!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.55,0:12:38.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There wasn’t as much of\Na shock as I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.06,0:12:40.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot… It’s only the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.32,0:12:41.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.13,0:12:53.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What’s that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.33,0:12:55.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s the next part!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.12,0:12:58.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Flower-Crane Cannon Launch\NMethod Two involves two steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:02.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The First Spell controls everything\Nfrom the launch to the directional setting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.23,0:13:06.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Secondary Spell then controls\Nthe acceleration and axis adjustment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.73,0:13:09.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,After that, you gradually\Nimprove the accuracy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.42,0:13:10.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.56,0:13:13.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t get in the way if you want\Nto get there safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.29,0:13:14.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Uh…Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.58,0:13:17.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There’s something\NI want to tell you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.71,0:13:23.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In order to enter the Seireitei,\Nwe have to stabilize this cannonball.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.93,0:13:26.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We must keep the spiritual energy\Noutput by each person
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.40,0:13:29.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,at a constant level.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.18,0:13:33.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To do that, if you keep\Nyour hand on this thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.34,0:13:36.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you’ll be able to see how much\Nenergy the others are releasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:39.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to adjust\Nyour energy release accordingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.91,0:13:40.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.91,0:13:40.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.27,0:13:44.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,One mistake and it’ll be the end.\NI’m counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:46.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.10,0:13:46.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.62,0:13:51.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Flower-Crane Cannon Launch\NMethod Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.96,0:13:53.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Secondary Spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:56.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fate of three sparrows,\Nfate of four dragons,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.70,0:13:59.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Blocked in from five directions,\Nunable to return six miles,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.83,0:14:01.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wind of the heavens,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.33,0:14:02.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Orangutan.\NSpoons, Cane of elm…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.37,0:14:06.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kurosaki…\NYou’re releasing a little too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.85,0:14:09.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A-Am I? S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.93,0:14:15.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki! Lower it some more!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.10,0:14:18.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-I know!\NI’ve lowered it a lot already!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.16,0:14:20.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.08,0:14:21.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I said I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.08,0:14:23.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A thousand sprinkles of ash,\Na thousand bits of wisdom…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.44,0:14:24.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.44,0:14:25.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The measure of white clouds…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.12,0:14:26.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I said I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.19,0:14:26.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Approaching the great darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.43,0:14:28.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not stepping on scarlet shadows…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.50,0:14:28.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m turning it down now. Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.48,0:14:30.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A thousand sprinkles of ashes,\Na thousand bits of wisdom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.50,0:14:35.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!\NYou made me read the same line twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:38.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So what?! Is that supposed\Nto be my fault too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.98,0:14:41.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’re making so much\Nnoise flapping that trap of yours
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.62,0:14:43.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that I lost my concentration,\Nyou numbskull!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.62,0:14:48.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Ichigo! Ganju…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.23,0:14:50.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be doing that, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.81,0:14:52.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She’s right. Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.74,0:14:53.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.97,0:14:55.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:58.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey… Outside…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.33,0:15:03.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s Seireitei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.25,0:15:14.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What’s that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.44,0:15:18.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Urgent alert! Urgent alert!\NIntruders in Seireitei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.31,0:15:21.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All Squads get into position! Repeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:23.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Urgent alert! Urgent alert!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.81,0:15:23.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Intruders?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.16,0:15:26.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be those Ryoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.16,0:15:27.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Intruders in Seireitei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.57,0:15:34.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Intruders in Seireitei!\NAll Squads get into position!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.95,0:15:41.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait, Kenpachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.58,0:15:52.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ken-chan…!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.91,0:15:53.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yachiru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.13,0:15:57.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? The enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.87,0:15:58.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’re going to kill them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.17,0:16:00.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It’s the Ryoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.05,0:16:02.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know how,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.58,0:16:05.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but it’s someone who fought\Nagainst Ichimaru and survived!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:07.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want to fight him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.24,0:16:12.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There is no choice…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.82,0:16:16.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This meeting of Squad Captains\Nis dismissed for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.90,0:16:20.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I shall inform you later how Ichimaru\Nwill be dealt with.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.71,0:16:28.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All Squads will report immediately\Nto their battle stations!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.37,0:16:48.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The warning certainly came…\Nat a good time for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.24,0:16:51.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t understand very well…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:54.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,what you’re trying to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.71,0:16:58.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can get away with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.16,0:17:03.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’d better not…take me too lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.32,0:17:37.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.76,0:17:41.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt it will be able to get through\Nthe Soul Shield Membrane…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.58,0:17:44.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll order everyone to draw back,\Njust in case!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.28,0:17:47.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-It’s coming this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.12,0:17:47.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.28,0:17:56.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:17:57.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.74,0:18:00.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, pour in all the\Nspiritual energy you’ve got!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.63,0:18:22.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It crashed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:25.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It ran into the Shield and stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.05,0:18:29.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To crash there and not be destroyed…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.80,0:18:33.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be a body of spiritual power\Nof such great concentration?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.70,0:18:41.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come on…!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.59,0:18:58.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What’s going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.50,0:19:00.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We got through the shield all right…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.37,0:19:03.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but why aren’t we falling to the ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.25,0:19:05.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t get separated!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.03,0:19:08.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Cannonball dissolved\Nwhen it hit the shield
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.69,0:19:11.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and it’s only temporarily holding us up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.24,0:19:13.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That means…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.13,0:19:17.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It will eventually create a whirlpool,\Nthen explode and vanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.69,0:19:18.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.83,0:19:24.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If we are separated at that time,\Nwe will be blown apart by the shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.31,0:19:25.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.31,0:19:25.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ohh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.75,0:19:37.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.58,0:19:39.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ohhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.93,0:19:44.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn…! I’m not gonna get…\Nblown away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.02,0:19:50.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t come near me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.10,0:19:52.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Go away, if you don’t like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:55.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Will you two cut it out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.62,0:20:00.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Grab onto whoever is nearest to you!\NDon’t let go, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.31,0:20:01.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.31,0:20:03.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.16,0:20:07.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let me sit on your shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.69,0:20:08.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yoruichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.15,0:20:11.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida…!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.69,0:20:17.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chad…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.68,0:20:21.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chad…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.79,0:20:27.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chad…!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.06,0:20:29.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:30.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,C-Chad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.79,0:20:39.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t worry. He will surely survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.79,0:20:42.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But if you want to be able to search\Nfor him down there,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.40,0:20:44.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you must consider\Nyour own safety first!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.54,0:20:50.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it…!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.67,0:20:52.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo…!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.17,0:20:55.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue…!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.94,0:21:07.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn… They split up into four!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.24,0:21:10.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Which one is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.66,0:21:24.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The strongest one…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.21,0:21:28.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Which one is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.56,0:21:46.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With much appreciation
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.44,0:21:48.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,send a rhapsody filled\Nwith treasured thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.77,0:21:52.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To the people who have\Nalways held me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.19,0:21:54.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.35,0:21:56.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.39,0:21:58.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever I may be
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.39,0:22:00.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll always be grateful for who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.48,0:22:03.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was casually walking through town
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.73,0:22:05.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Around the time dusk fell\Nand the city was bathed in red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.81,0:22:07.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was an afternoon with\Ncrowds of people coming and going
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.02,0:22:09.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know why but\NI just stood there and watched
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.81,0:22:12.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then my cell phone started to vibrate\Nand I made myself move
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.39,0:22:14.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,hoping it could fill\Nin this hole in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.39,0:22:16.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’re not alone\NYou see, everybody
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.52,0:22:18.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta hold each other up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.56,0:22:20.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With much appreciation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.90,0:22:23.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I send a rhapsody filled\Nwith treasured thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.23,0:22:26.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To the people who have\Nalways held me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.35,0:22:28.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.39,0:22:30.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.56,0:22:32.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever I may be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.48,0:22:34.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll always be grateful for who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.16,0:22:39.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!\NI'll go and take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.61,0:22:41.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But my Zabimaru is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.18,0:22:42.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know where it is,\NHinamori?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.44,0:22:45.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I think someone was using it\Nto slice some pickled radish.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.35,0:22:48.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Roar, Zabimaru!\NChop up that radish!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.27,0:22:50.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hasn't your character changed\Na lot, recently?